 <strong>scale</strong></h4>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">크기</code> / 없음 (배수 사용)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>scale(x, y): 크기(x축, y축)</li>\n<li>scaleX(x): 크기(x축)</li>\n<li>scaleY(y): 크기(y축)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>한쪽 축만 명시하면 찌그러질 수 있기 때문애<br />\n보통은 크기 제어 시 x, y 축을 모두 명시함</p>\n<h4 id=\"3-rotate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-rotate\" aria-label=\"3 rotate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(3) <strong>rotate</strong></h4>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">회전</code> / deg 단위 사용</p>\n<ul>\n<li>rotate(degree): 회전(각도)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"4-skew\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-skew\" aria-label=\"4 skew permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(4) <strong>skew</strong></h4>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">기울임</code> / deg 단위 사용</p>\n<ul>\n<li>skew(x, y): 기울임(x축, y축)</li>\n<li>skewX(x): 기울임(x축)</li>\n<li>skewY(y): 기울임(y축)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"5-matrix\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-matrix\" aria-label=\"5 matrix permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focu